# Purpose
The purpose of the instructions created for this use case is to consolidate various sources of Microsoft Copilot updates (and related products) into a single distilled repository worksheet inside an Excel workbook. 
Once created, the ongoing sections will generate a timeline of when the updates will land and several additional worksheets that focus on the actions to be performed by deployment, adoption and admin teams in relation to the updates.

# Prerequisites
Microsoft 365 Copilot Premium licence and access to the Microsoft Excel agent.

# Method
For best results use either the Microsoft Excel agent in Copilot Chat, @ mention the Excel agent from Copilot Chat or use the instructions directly in the Copilot sidebar of the Excel application (web or desktop).
Copy and paste the text (or click on Copy raw file) from the instruction files into Copilot.
